The food suck here and the dumplings are not even dumplings they are giant bread things and their meat are totally not fresh and have been kept in a frozen place also the dough is as thick as 3 pieces of paper or even more, never come to this restaurant!!!🤯🤯🤯🤮🤮🤮🤮
最愛這裡的涼拌米線，足料夠大份。但只限荃灣總店，其他分店認真一般
我最喜歡的米綫，湯底每次都喝光光
